{"tid":392742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗洗衣工場？","createTime":"2017-09-08T16:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T08:54:53.000Z","uid":108785,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ffdd4c947242041ae6bdf902e6cf2f9d5e13d0fc","tid":392742,"uid":108785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T16:40:30.000Z","msg":"元朗洗夜工場？含撚啦<br />\n<br />\n之前同三個FD返過 500蚊人工 返8到6點 住天水圍嘅都要成六點起身汁野食早餐 去到7點9等報名 7點59分去到照當你遲到<br />\n<br />\n有朋友一齊返嘅時候小不免都會有傾計嘅時候都算<br />\n<br />\n比佢見到就會同間外判公司嘅大粒野話佢都傾計 唔撚專心做野 但問題做嘅野將啲公司（污穢衫）汁出黎 咁做野時都要傾計笑下做下咁 <br />\n<br />\n間工場啲人都未出聲話我地唔認真做野時 班仆街外判就先告狀 同自己外判啲掃把督尻我地背脊 再者 報左更返工嘅時候 突然刪撚左我地個名 就話因爲你地比工場啲人投訴.....<br />\n<br />\n想返嘅可以試水溫 話就話輕鬆野 實際上做野做唔停 10個鐘入面除左食飯都唔會有得休息 即使你做到身水身汗 都要照做 <br />\n<br />\n唔好話我做唔做得黎 唔好話份份工都係咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf789400e754888d07dc4578284a4b2f361c4473","tid":392742,"uid":145320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T16:57:16.000Z","msg":"試過報更 報完del左我個名無得翻<br />\n嬲到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾工 狗也不屌另外都發現唔少黑材料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 利申 翻左3日"},{"pid":"b03d9ef3c9289593127f2f785abe0eae0f5663c3","tid":392742,"uid":108785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:58:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過報更 報完del左我個名無得翻<br />\n嬲到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾工 狗也不屌另外都發現唔少黑材料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 利申 翻左3日</blockquote><br />\n間外判啲人好撚閪"},{"pid":"f49deace4565e00fe29ae612f8dc4e3a996be3ad","tid":392742,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T18:15:14.000Z","msg":"比着我即日走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e379684f3963ad0d48d42c839b127404eef5cb24","tid":392742,"uid":108785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T18:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比着我即日走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心閪工黎"},{"pid":"f1e3e0c307c6af922364c8b961bd9c101eaf0b22","tid":392742,"uid":32425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T19:08:29.000Z","msg":"伏 中一次就要醒覺<br />\n<br />\n$500 / 10hrs<br />\n<br />\n真係值得你咁樣出賣青春？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef7a01df31c86b365a12734d27bd3f4e70fc9a5","tid":392742,"uid":52499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T19:18:10.000Z","msg":"返過3日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ec1ff8cf06c7f597f57702b9b6d3fc3e659d3f","tid":392742,"uid":113465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T19:57:53.000Z","msg":"元朗自設嘅大工場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db634102eee72a18511160f0be5e7d688caf615b","tid":392742,"uid":141641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T04:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>元朗自設嘅大工場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生曬原味靠曬個太陽"},{"pid":"8abecec5ace9ef72c9893369bc79bf189f7c6687","tid":392742,"uid":65526,"